541d2498-493a-4887-aa6b-1a91c2ef56e7.do_description: To make the output, you have to...extend each red dot straight up so it forms a vertical line. The red pixel must change direction as it reaches the grey pixel to the right and continue straight up.
541d2498-493a-4887-aa6b-1a91c2ef56e7.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input size
541d2498-493a-4887-aa6b-1a91c2ef56e7.see_description: In the input, you should see...two grey pixels and three red pixels

6d419aed-385e-4be9-83a3-98e41a745952.do_description: To make the output, you have to...extend the red pixels to the top of the grid from the bottom, take the red pixel around the gray pixel through the right to get to the top.
6d419aed-385e-4be9-83a3-98e41a745952.grid_description: The output grid size... as the same as the input grid
6d419aed-385e-4be9-83a3-98e41a745952.see_description: In the input, you should see... three Red and three gray pixels scattered at the middle of the grid.

ab972557-fb76-4d70-9469-18067fa6a7ea.do_description: To make the output, you have to...extend each red dot straight up so it forms a line to the top of the grid. If the red line would go through a gray square, the line must go to the right of it and then continue going straight up, making it a bent line.
ab972557-fb76-4d70-9469-18067fa6a7ea.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the original
ab972557-fb76-4d70-9469-18067fa6a7ea.see_description: In the input, you should see...several red dots and several gray dots

bdd0290d-dab9-4841-9fc1-df519906efab.do_description: To make the output, you have to...draw a straight line with the base of the red dot. If the red dot line goes through a grey dot , you have to stop the red line and start it again at the right side of the grey dot and continue it.
bdd0290d-dab9-4841-9fc1-df519906efab.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input grid size.
bdd0290d-dab9-4841-9fc1-df519906efab.see_description: In the input, you should see...several red and grey dots.
